OL,6,FA teenager warned "today is the day"
OL,7,Fin a series of sinister messages on
OL,8,Fsocial media before walking into a
OL,9,Fschool and stabbing a girl with a
OL,10,Fpiece of broken glass, a court has
OL,11,Fheard.
OL,13,FSheffield Crown Court heard the 17-
OL,14,Fyear-old - who cannot be named for
OL,15,Flegal reasons - also wrote a post
OL,16,Fwarning a member of staff "don't come
OL,17,Fin today" before the incident at
OL,18,FBirley Academy in Sheffield.
