OL,3,CTeen warned 'today's the day' before
OL,4,Cattack in school, court told
OL,6,FThe court heard the girls were unable
OL,7,Fto get into any classrooms, which had
OL,8,Fbeen barricaded, and hid in a toilet
OL,9,Fwhile the defendant continued with the
OL,10,Fattack.
OL,12,FMs Rafter said: "He was heard saying,
OL,13,F'I hate this school.'"
OL,15,FThe court heard how the youth mentor
OL,16,Fthen tried to restrain the boy and
OL,17,Frecalled him saying, "This was meant
OL,18,Fto happen" and "You don't know who I
OL,19,Fam".
